flowchart LR
    subgraph Envelope ["Sweet-Spot Envelope (8 Joint Conditions)"]
        direction TB
        C1[Workload narrowness<br/>7B–32B specialist sufficient]
        C2[Reward verifiability<br/>or judge reliability controls]
        C3[Token volume<br/>≥50M/mo premium<br/>≥500M/mo mid-tier]
        C4[Workflow stability<br/>≥12 months in scope]
        C5[Inference-stack capability<br/>vLLM/SGLang/multi-LoRA]
        C6[Regulatory regime fit<br/>ε ≥ 4 viable today]
        C7[EU compute<br/>< 1/3 base training]
        C8[12–18 month durability window<br/>re-fine-tune budgeted]
    end

    Inputs([Workload + Operator]) --> Envelope
    Envelope --> Decision{All 8 satisfied?}
    Decision -- Yes --> Recipe[Execute Recipe<br/>GRPO + SFT-distill +<br/>RULER + 9-layer inference]
    Decision -- No --> Fallback[Frontier API + prompt<br/>engineering]

    Recipe --> Outcomes[Break-even:<br/>50M tok/mo @ 7mo<br/>vs premium APIs<br/>500M tok/mo @ 14mo<br/>vs mid-tier APIs]

    style Envelope fill:#eef
    style Recipe fill:#9f9,stroke:#393
    style Fallback fill:#ffc,stroke:#960
    style Outcomes fill:#cef,stroke:#069
